        {
            "title": "亞洲外匯走弱,印度盧比創歷史新低,伊朗戰爭令油市憂慮持續",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tDAy3tVkjTc8s8ypZjXbhA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/Indian_Rupee_M_1440056047.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 週五大多數亞洲貨幣下跌,印度盧比創下歷史新低,市場仍對美國-以色列對伊朗戰爭引發的能源市場中斷感到不安。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元走強,並將連續第二週上漲,因市場押注能源推動的通脹將阻止聯準會在短期內降息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場對美國放寬對購買俄羅斯石油的更多限制反應有限,原油價格在亞洲交易中收窄早盤跌幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大多數區域貨幣本週均錄得跌幅,亞洲經濟體因嚴重依賴進口而被視為極易受到石油市場中斷的影響。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>日圓觸及近兩年低點,亞洲外匯走弱</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日圓兌美元USD/JPY上漲0.1%至159.48日圓,為2024年7月以來的最高水平。報導顯示,東京正考慮釋放緊急石油儲備,該國也在尋求替代原油來源。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-37b41496-323e-3fe7-998c-4f931db179bd-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日圓是本週亞洲表現最差的貨幣,USDJPY上漲1%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">韓元兌美元USD/KRW週五小幅下跌,但本週上漲0.5%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳元兌美元AUD/USD下跌0.2%,但由於市場越來越確信澳洲儲備銀行將在下週加息,本週將錄得溫和漲幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新台幣兌美元USD/TWD上漲0.3%,而新加坡元兌美元USD/SGD持平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">人民幣本週表現優於其他貨幣,美元兌人民幣USD/CNY週五上漲0.2%,但本週將下跌0.2%。中國被視為能很好地抵禦石油市場的短期供應衝擊。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>印度盧比因石油供應擔憂創歷史新低</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印度盧比兌美元USD/INR上漲0.1%,並短暫觸及92.522盧比的歷史高點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據報導,印度儲備銀行的干預遏制了盧比的更大跌幅,儘管如此,USDINR本週仍將上漲0.5%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鑑於印度約80%的石油消費依賴進口,該貨幣以及更廣泛的印度市場受到油價上漲擔憂的打擊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當地媒體報導還指出,該國正面臨天然氣短缺問題。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>美元將錄得週度漲幅,PCE數據待公布</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元指數和美元指數期貨在亞洲交易中小幅上漲,將連續第二週上漲0.8%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元受到避險需求增加的支撐,市場擔心油價持續上漲將加劇通脹黏性,促使聯準會採取更鷹派的立場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場基本上已降低對聯準會未來幾個月降息的押注,CME Fedwatch顯示至少在9月之前不會有任何變化。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">PCE價格指數數據——聯準會偏好的通脹指標——將於週五公布,預計將提供更多通脹線索。但該數據為1月份的數據,不太可能反映油價上漲帶來的任何通脹上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AF%E8%B5%B0%E5%BC%B1-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E7%9B%A7%E6%AF%94%E5%89%B5%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%8E-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E4%BB%A4%E6%B2%B9%E5%B8%82%E6%86%82%E6%85%AE%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C-054231513.html",
